<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Kerry Katona was seen to break down in tears as her boyfriend Ryan Mahoney popped the question during their Spanish holiday last week. </p>

<p>The former Atomic Kitten star was ringing in her 40th birthday when the hunky personal trainer, 31, dropped down on one knee in front of her delighted children during their idyllic summer break at the Silverfield Villa in Granada. </p>

<p>Sporting an elegant red dress, the blonde beauty could not contain her delight as she was presented with the eye-popping diamond.</p>

